[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14008] updated osc_633 string escaping
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13996] allowed both slash and backslash for Windows paths
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13968] enabled bools to be type checked with each other
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13962] updated the human-date-parser crate
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13961] tried a potential fix for vt processing
