, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13985] updated the merge example
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13842] improved startup time when using std-lib
akirabaruah 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13955] implemented consistent default key bindings for ide_completion_menu
