[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13998] fixed footer truncation in nu-table for head_on_border cases
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13964] fixed :try table view in nu-explore
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13952] fixed coloring of file names in 
``ls | explore``
Lord-LightSpeed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13993] updated 
``fill.rs``
 to fix the last example in help
Kither12 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13988] added dollar sign escaping in tab completion
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13980] fixed typos
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13974] simplified the Dockerfile
